                    <rdg resp="#oliverioDAI1">ἐλ<supplied reason="lost">αῖαι</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">ἔλαιον</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <note>such a restoration would be too long</note></rdg>
